(feat) 2026-03-19 – §5 Project/Solution, §9 DTE Events, §10 Options, §12 TodoTagger

feat(ProjectService): add Project & Solution APIs (Section 5)
feat(EventService): add DTE Events subscription (Section 9)
feat(OptionsService): add Settings/Options page (Section 10)
feat(TodoTagger): add MEF Text Adornment & Tagger (Section 12)

Nguyên nhân:
  Tiếp tục triển khai các phần còn lại của VS2017-Extension-API-Reference.md
  từ Section 5 đến Section 12 (bỏ qua §6-§7-§8-§11 đã được xử lý riêng hoặc
  không cần wrapper service vì đã có trong VSCommandTable/ShowToolWindow).

Thay đổi chính:
  NEW src/Services/ProjectService.cs
    - GetSolutionInfo, GetAllProjects, GetActiveDocumentProject
    - GetReferencesOfActiveProject (VSLangProj.VSProject)
    - GetProjectItemsOfActiveProject (recursive)
    - GetActiveBuildConfig, BuildSolution, CleanSolution
    - DTOs: SolutionInfo, ProjectInfo, ReferenceInfo, ProjectItemInfo, BuildConfigInfo

  NEW src/Services/EventService.cs
    - Subscribe/Unsubscribe: BuildEvents, SolutionEvents, DocumentEvents,
      WindowEvents, SelectionEvents, DebuggerEvents
    - Giữ strong field references (tránh GC)
    - EventFired: Action<string> cho UI layer
    - IDisposable auto-unsubscribe

  NEW src/Services/OptionsService.cs
    - SampleOptionsPage : DialogPage (4 settings)
    - OptionsService: typed accessors + OpenOptionsDialog()
    - MyPackage: [ProvideOptionPage] attribute

  NEW src/Tagging/TodoTagger.cs
    - MEF ITaggerProvider + ITagger<TextMarkerTag>
    - ContentType="text", singleton per buffer
    - Highlight "TODO" tokens, invalidate on change
    - IDisposable

  MOD src/ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowState.cs – +Project, +Events, +Options
  MOD src/MyPackage.cs – wire 3 new services, Dispose, ProvideOptionPage
  MOD src/ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowControl.xaml – 12 new buttons
  MOD src/ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowControl.xaml.cs – 12 new handlers
  MOD src/AsyncToolWindowSample.csproj – +VSLangProj ref, +4 Compile entries

  NEW docs/tutorials/project-events-options-tagger_2026-03-19.md
  MOD CHANGELOG.md
  MOD README.md

Tác dụng:
  - Tất cả §5 §9 §10 §12 đã có UI buttons trong Tool Window.
  - TodoTagger tự động highlight "TODO" trong mọi file text (MEF, không cần click).
  - EventService subscribe được build/solution/document/window/selection/debugger events.
  - Options page xuất hiện tại Tools › Options › Async Tool Window Sample › General.
  - VSLangProj reference thêm để hỗ trợ References API (phải resolve qua VS PrivateAssemblies).

